<div class="container" id="card">
  <h1>‚ù§Ô∏è Aditi ‚ù§Ô∏è</h1>
  <h2>Will you be my Valentine? üíñ</h2>

  <div class="buttons">
    <button id="yesBtn">Yes!</button>
    <button id="noBtn">Really?</button>
  </div>

  <div class="quote">
    "Every moment with you feels like a dream come true."
  </div>
